race.comment: PETIT MAMSELLE (1) was unwanted in betting last start but proved too quick with an all-the-way win over 460m at this track in a Maiden, scoring by 5.5 lengths (26.05). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Expected to measure up again. POINT BREAK (3) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (30.56) at The Meadows. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Expected to give a good account. DEVIL'S SYMPATHY (8) ran below best last time finishing sixth (25.55) over 450m at Shepparton in a Mix 6/7. Can measure up this time. ROWDY BOY (4) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.
